long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome-Extension allows our apps to connect and interact with the "Genesys Cloud" web application. 

Why "dingsConnctor"?
- Web applications are sandboxed and confined to reside inside a browser
- Web applications and their host machine only have limited ability to interact with each other

Please check out our apps and contact us for more information...
